  "description": "<p>Fast and light doesn\u2019t need to equal a cold night. This lightweight quilt is generously filled with 800-fill-power goose down, wrapping you in channels of pillowy warmth. Integrated pad pockets and straps, let you secure the quilt to your sleeping pad, so you stay on your pad and your quilt stays on you. The enclosed footbox keeps your feet happy and warm, making socks to bed an option, not a must. Adding the Talon quilt to your sleep system makes summer backpacking easier, lighter, and comfier.</p><ul><li>800-fill-power grey goose down has an incredible warmth to weight ratio and is super packable</li><li>Goose down is ethically sourced and meets the Responsible Down Standard for animal welfare</li><li>Box baffle construction offers improved warmth, loft, and packability, when compared to traditional quilting</li><li>Lightweight recycled nylon material is Bluesign approved and uses a tight \u201cdownproof\u201d weave, so the feathers stay right where they should be</li><li>PFC-free DWR finish helps the quilt shake off morning dew and keeps it cleaner, longer</li><li>Enclosed footbox dimensions: 32 x 34cm</li><li>Included roll-top stuff sack and storage cube</li></ul>",
